============================
WassrMinus
============================

What's this
----------------------------

WassrMinnus is poor Wassr client.
It includes core module, and simple script and command line tool to access Wassr.

What's Wassr
----------------------------

Micro blog service like Twitter. 

http://wassr.com/

How to use
----------------------------

First of all, you have to configure config file($WassrMinus/etc/config.yml)


See Also
----------------------------

* Wassr
** http://wassr.com/
* Wassr API Document
** http://wassr.com/help/api/
